title: Rent a Kuat Piston Pro X 2-Bike Rack - 2” Hitch
description: Looking to rent my Kuat Piston Pro X 2-Bike Rack - 2” Hitch . Let me know if you're interested! [BREAK] The Kuat Piston Pro X Hitch Rack is a premium 2-bike carrier designed for serious cyclists; It features a robust stainless steel and metal construction, accommodating bikes with wheelbases up to 53"" and tire sizes from 18"" to 29""; With a maximum load capacity of 67 lbs. 2"" hitch, it's perfect for transporting heavy e-bikes and mountain bikes.   Semi-integrated high-strand 12 mm cable lock has plenty of length for the wheels and frames of all your bikes.   Integrated, low-profile LED taillights synchronize with your vehicle's brake and turn signals, providing enhanced rear visibility on the road, whether rack is folded or flat  Magnetic cable docking makes setup easy—just snap in the magnetic cable and plug the 4-Pin into your vehicle's trailer outlet
